dct_title_s: A new and improved map of Ireland exhibiting the rail coach and turnpike roads, the lakes, rivers & canals, the principal ranges of mountains : also the borough &. market towns, with their distances from the capital
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Includes list of counties with population and number of Members of Parliament. Date of publication from Tooley's dictionary of mapmakers. Originally issued folded in covers 20 x 11 cm.
